comments: McDaniels (MIN) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Doncic (DAL) on the wing.
McDaniels (MIN) makes contact with the ball and the part of Doncic's (DAL) hand that is on the ball, partially dislodging it from Doncic on the wing.
McDaniels (MIN) brings his left arm forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Doncic's (DAL) side as Doncic spins into the lane.
McDaniels (MIN) initiates contact across Doncic's (DAL) left arm and affects his driving shot attempt prior to the block.
Bullock (DAL) and Edwards (MIN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Bullock (DAL) brings his right arm forward and marginal contact occurs Edwards' (MIN) front at the top of the perimeter.
Bullock (DAL) maintains a rested forearm on Edwards' (MIN) right side and releases away without applying any force as Edwards starts his upward shooting motion.
Anderson (MIN) moves toward the basket after the release of the shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Doncic (DAL) as Doncic secures the rebound.
Anderson (MIN) brings his left arm toward Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs with Doncic's front as he accelerates on the wing.
Green (DAL) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Anderson (MIN) is already in Doncic's (DAL) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs when they come together during the drive.
Anderson (MIN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Doncic (DAL) prior to any incidental contact occurring.
Ntilikina (DAL) and Anderson (MIN) engage and disengage with one another after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) brushes Doncic's (DAL) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Doncic secures the rebound and simultaneously passes.
Irving (DAL) is already in McDaniels' (MIN) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together in the lane.
McDaniels (MIN) fumbles the ball and upon regaining possession, maintains his pivot foot.
Irving (DAL) raises his right arm and initiates contact with McDaniels' (MIN) left arm, affecting the layup attempt.

Edwards (MIN) brings his left arm toward Irving's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs with Irving's front as he drives inside the perimeter. Edwards then uses his right hand to make clean contact with the ball, momentarily dislodging it from Irving.
Conley (MIN) brushes Irving's (DAL) right arm and marginal contact occurs at the end of Irving's drive.
Green (DAL) commits a take foul on Conley (MIN).
Doncic (DAL) enters the lane prior to the release of Conley's (MIN) free throw attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) and Doncic (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
McDaniels (MIN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Doncic (DAL) during the inbound.
McDaniels (MIN) brings his forearm toward Doncic's (DAL) right side and marginal contact occurs as Doncic retrieves the loose ball.
Edwards (MIN) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Irving (DAL) and marginal body contact occurs with Irving as he passes.
Prince (MIN) and Pinson (DAL) come together at the same spot off-ball and marginal side-to-side contact occurs prior to Prince stealing the pass.
Irving (DAL) brushes Prince's (MIN) left side and marginal contact occurs following the steal.
